<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
        <title>EMA623_06_SU_0003_s</title>

        <!-- 공통 js-->
        <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

        <!-- 공통 css-->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css"/>

        <!-- 개별 -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema623_common.css"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema623_06.css"/>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="app_wrap" class="ema623_06_SU_0003">
            <section class="title type2">
                <h2 data-head="1_pink" lang="y">쌓기나무로 호텔 모양을 만들었습니다. 호텔 모양을 층별로 나타내는 방법을 알아봅시다.</h2>
            </section>

            <section class="contents paging_layout">
                <article class="page page_1 ">
                    <div class="img_row">
                        <div class="img_wrap">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0003_contents.png" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 lang="y">쌓기나무로 만들면 어떤 모양이 될지 예상해 보고, 만들어 보세요</h3>
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0003_contents2.png" alt=""/>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                </article>
                <article class="page page_2">
                    <div class="img_row">
                        <div class="img_wrap"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0003_img01.png" alt=""/></div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <div>
                                <h3 lang="y">똑같은 모양으로 만드는 데 필요한 쌓기나무는 몇 개인가요?</h3>
                                <!-- 단답형 -->
                                <div class="question_box gap_8 justify_center">
                                    <div class="input_wrap short_width">
                                        <math-field
                                            data-answer-single="10"
                                            placeholder="​"
                                            contenteditable="true"
                                            tabindex="0"
                                            id="page_4-math-field-3"
                                            sound="false"
                                            math-mode-space="\:"
                                            smart-fence="off"
                                            smart-superscript="off"></math-field>
                                        <div class="text_hint">10
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <span lang="y">개</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_3">
                  <div class="img_row building_blocks">
                    <div class="img_wrap"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0003_contents.png" alt=""/></div>

                    <div class="input_area">
                        <div>
                            <h3 lang="y">쌓기나무로 만들면 어떤 모양이 될지 예상해 보고, 만들어 보세요</h3>
                            <div class="gray_box">
                                <div class="box_title">
                                    <button class="minus"></button>쌓기나무 개수<button class="plus"></button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="wood_box_area">
                                    <button class="wood_box"></button>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap_12 justify_center mt_20">
                              <span class="dropdown_text">모양이</span>
                              <div class="dropdown_wrap flex justify_center mb_30 ">
                                  <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="같습니다.">
                                      <option></option>
                                      <!--최초선택데이터 생성 방지용-->
                                      <option value="같습니다."></option>
                                      <option value="다릅니다."></option>
                                  </select>
                              </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_4">
                  <div class="input_area">
                    <div>
                        <h3 lang="y">층별로 나타내는 방법의 좋은 점을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                            <ol class="example_box">
                                <li lang="y">모양이 한 가지로만 만들어지기 때문에 만든 모양을 정확하게 알 수 있습니다.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </article>

                <div class="btn_area">
                    <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                    <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                    <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                    <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>